MATCH_TOOL: Edit|Write
MATCH_PATTERN: packages/game-cartridges/src/machines/index\.ts
ADVISORY: |
  game-cartridges has TWO barrel export levels:
  1. packages/game-cartridges/src/machines/index.ts (machine registry)
  2. packages/game-cartridges/src/index.ts (package entry point)
  Adding a new machine to machines/index.ts is NOT enough — you must
  ALSO add it to src/index.ts or it won't be available to consumers
  via import('@pecking-order/game-cartridges').
